HEADWORD: Xeriff
<hw>Xer"iff</hw> <pr>(z⟦ecr⟧r"⟦icr⟧f)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Shereef</er>.]</ety> <def>A gold coin formerly current in Egypt and
